    <span class="logo">SWISS FIREFIGHTERS</span><br/>
    <span class="slogan">portail web des sapeurs pompiers suisses</span>
    <br/>
</p>
<p class="infos">
    <a href="http://www.swiss-firefighters.ch/">www.swiss-firefighters.ch</a><br/>
    <a href="http://www.facebook.com/swissfirefighters">facebook.com/swissfirefighters</a>
</p>

</body>
